 that no rival has come close to matching across the full breadth of its in=
ternational footprint. Revenue has compounded at nearly 21% annually over t=
he past decade, and the margin profile has transformed from breakeven to ge=
nuinely exceptional as the fixed cost of content gets spread across an ever=
-larger subscriber base.</p>
<p style=3D"Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:non=
