ica, arial, sans-serif;line-height:24px;color:#333333;font-size:16px">The c=
ompetitive position is harder to replicate than the subscriber count alone =
suggests. Netflix has spent two decades building a content library, recomme=
ndation engine, and production infrastructure that functions as a single in=
tegrated system. The algorithm learns from the viewing behavior of hundreds=
 of millions of users to surface the right content at the right moment, whi=
ch reduces churn and increases the perceived value of the subscription in w=
ays that are invisible in any single financial metric. No new entrant can b=
uy that data advantage. It compounds only with time and scale.</p>
<p style=3D"Margin:0;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;-ms-text-size-adjust:non=
