argin story is the most important financial development of the past five ye=
ars. Net income margins have expanded from effectively zero a decade ago to=
 22% in the trailing year, with the forward model projecting further expans=
ion toward 33% as revenue grows faster than the content and technology cost=
 base beneath it. That trajectory is not a function of cutting investment. =
Netflix continues to spend heavily on content. It is a function of operatin=
g leverage at a scale the business has only recently reached.</p></td>
